QuestData.Title: Old Friends
QuestData.Description: Admiral Taylor was ordered to establish a garrison inland while we erected yours in Shadowmoon Valley. He settled just a short ways north of here.$B$BThe two of us could go there and borrow some supplies to tide us over before our next shipment.$B$BWhat do you say, commander? I'm sure the admiral will be thrilled to see you again.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Jasper Fel at Admiral Taylor's Garrison.
QuestData.RewardText: What in the king's name happened here?
